Function Reference/get blogaddress by domain « WordPress Codex
-----------

Get a full blog URL, given a domain and a path.

Usage
-----

` <?php get_blogaddress_by_domain( $domain, $path ) ?> `

Parameters
----------

 `$domain` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*) The domain
    Default: *None*

 `$path` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*) The path
    Default: *None*

Return Values
-------------

 `` `(string)`{style="color:gray"} 
:   The full blog URL

Examples
--------

Notes
-----

Change Log
----------

Since: [3.0.0](/Version_3.0 "Version 3.0")

Source File
-----------

get\_blogaddress\_by\_domain() is located in `wp-includes/ms-blogs.php`

